import React from 'react'
import SideBar from './containers/SideBar'
import Main from './containers/Main'
import { StyledApp, GlobalStyle } from './styles/styles'
import FlexRow from './containers/FlexRow'
import ShowValue from './components/ShowValue'

function App() {
    return (
        <>
            <GlobalStyle />
            <StyledApp>
                <SideBar>
                    <nav>Transactions</nav>
                </SideBar>
                <Main>
                    <FlexRow>
                        <ShowValue
                            color="#00b300"
                            value="999,00"
                            title="Balance"
                        />
                        <ShowValue
                            color="#00b300"
                            value="999,00"
                            title="Income"
                        />
                        <ShowValue
                            color="#e00000"
                            value="999,00"
                            title="Outcome"
                        />
                    </FlexRow>
                </Main>
            </StyledApp>
        </>
    )
}

export default App
